description: Returns all tags for the given Elasticsearch domain.

parameters.name: ARN
parameters.description: Specify the ARN for the Elasticsearch domain to which the tags are attached that you want to view.

nested_items.name: TagList
nested_items.description: List of Tag for the requested Elasticsearch domain.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: Specifies the TagKey, the name of the tag. Tag keys must be unique for the Elasticsearch domain to which they are attached.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: Specifies the TagValue, the value assigned to the corresponding tag key. Tag values can be null and do not have to be unique in a tag set. For example, you can have a key value pair in a tag set of project : Trinity and cost-center : Trinity.
